post_text:
St. Helens School District was awarded a School Health Services Planning Grant from the Oregon Health Authority. From now until May, we will be doing a needs assessment to identify:
- the health needs of our students and families;
- our community strengths;
- health resources available in our community;
- what additional supports are needed.

We need your help. Over the coming weeks, we will be reaching out to staff, students, and school communities to gather input through surveys, in-person focus groups, and interviews.

We have created an online survey for families and caregivers of students. Click on the following link to complete the survey:

https://forms.gle/7hFur3zann8XuH2e9

If you have any questions or would like to be part of an in-person focus group or interview, please feel free to reach out to Dr. Katy Wagner, SHHS Principal, at katyw@sthelens.k12.or.us or 503-397-1900.

